quran[9]{c,v,t,f}:
  34,23,"Kandi nta buvugizi buzagira icyo bumara kuri We (Allah), usibye gusa uwo yahaye uburenganzira. (Iyo Allah avuze, abamalayika barakangarana bakagwa igihumure) kugeza igihe imitima yabo ishiriye ubwoba, (bamwe) bakavuga bati “Nyagasani wanyu yavuze iki?” (Abandi) bati “(Yavuze) ukuri; kandi ni Uwikirenga, Usumba byose.”",""
  34,24,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ni nde ubaha amafunguro aturutse mu birere no mu isi?” Vuga uti “Ni Allah! Kandi mu by’ukuri, yaba twe cyangwa mwe (abahakanyi) hari abari mu nzira y’ukuri cyangwa mu buyobe bugaragara.”",""
  34,25,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Ntabwo muzabazwa ku byerekeye ibyaha twakoze, kandi natwe ntitubazwa ibyo mukora.”",""
  34,26,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Nyagasani wacu azaduhuriza hamwe twese (ku munsi w’imperuka), hanyuma adukiranure mu kuri; kuko ari We Mucamanza w’ikirenga, Umumenyi uhebuje.”",""
  34,27,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Nimunyereke ibigirwamana mwamubangikanyije na byo.” Nta na kimwe! Ahubwo We ni Allah (wenyine), Umunyacyubahiro bihebuje, Nyirubugenge buhambaye.",""
  34,28,"Kandi nta kindi cyatumye tukohereza usibye kuba utanga inkuru nziza no kuba umuburizi ku bantu bose; ariko abenshi mu bantu ntibabizi.",""
  34,29,"(Abahakanyi) baravuga bati “Ese ni ryari iri sezerano (imperuka) rizasohora niba koko muri abanyakuri?”",""
  34,30,"Vuga (yewe Muhamadi) uti “Isezerano ryanyu ni umunsi mudashobora gutinzaho isaha n’imwe cyangwa ngo muwihutishe.”",""
  34,31,"Kandi abahakanye baravuze bati “Ntidushobora kwemera iyi Qur’an ndetse n’ibyayibanjirije (ibitabo). Ariko iyo uza kubona ababangikanyamana bahagaritswe imbere ya Nyagasani wabo baterana amagambo; abanyantege nke babwira abibone bati “Iyo bitaza kuba mwe, rwose twari kuba turi abemeramana.”",""
